        <p>
		kō-vicaiya-para<unclear>mēc</unclear>cuvara-parumaṟku
		<lb n="2"/>yāṇṭu Oṉpat-āvatu
	</p>
        <p>
		<unclear>va</unclear>miṟaiyār vē
		<lb break="no" n="3"/>ṇāṭ-iḷa-k-kōvūr-nāṭṭu kō<choice>
            <orig>-I</orig>
            <reg>yi</reg>
          </choice>l paṭṭar van
		<lb break="no" n="4"/>tu toṟu-k koṇṭa nāṉṟu mēṟ-ceṅkai māmm-u
		<lb break="no" n="5"/>ṭaiya pāra
		<lb break="no" n="6"/>tāyar maka
		<lb break="no" n="7"/>ṉ toṟu mī
		<lb break="no" n="8"/>ṭṭu-p <supplied reason="undefined">paṭṭā</supplied>
		<lb break="no" n="9"/>ṉ mukaṉ
	</p>
